{"text_id":92802,"tokens":["We"," introduce"," a"," novel"," class"," of"," adjustment"," rules"," for"," a"," collection"," of"," beliefs","."," This"," is"," an"," extension"," of"," Lewis","'"," imaging"," to"," absorb"," probabilistic"," evidence"," in"," generalized"," settings","."," Unlike"," standard"," tools",","," our"," framework"," provides"," a"," direct"," treatment"," of"," beliefs"," that"," are"," unstable"," in"," the"," sense"," that"," they"," can"," be"," made"," arbitrarily"," close"," to"," any"," desired"," values",","," without"," the"," need"," for"," auxiliary"," assumptions"," or"," constructions","."," This"," feature"," is"," particularly"," important"," when"," a"," theory"," has"," a"," continuous"," spectrum"," of"," states"," and"," the"," set"," of"," states"," is"," not"," compact","."," Our"," framework"," can"," be"," used"," to"," deal"," with"," beliefs"," of"," the"," form"," \"","I"," believe"," that"," the"," state"," is"," close"," to"," x",".\""," We"," present"," an"," axio","matic"," character","ization"," of"," such"," beliefs"," and"," derive"," a"," representation"," theorem"," that"," identifies"," them"," as"," a"," product"," of"," a"," standard"," belief"," with"," the"," probability"," that"," the"," state"," is"," close"," to"," x","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"65B","label":1}